# -----------------------------------------------
# UMARV Hardware Repo — .gitignore of root / Template
# Covers Altium Designer auto-generated files
# -----------------------------------------------

# Altium history & previews (large, auto-regenerated)
History/
__Previews/
__Backup/
ProjectLogs/
Logs/

# Altium lock files (created when a file is open)
*.lck
*.Lck

# Altium auto-saved backups
*.bak
*.AutoSave

# Altium status/annotation files
*.~*
*.DXPPrjLog

# -----------------------------------------------
# What SHOULD be committed:
#   .SchDoc       — schematic
#   .PcbDoc       — PCB layout
#   .PrjPcb       — project file
#   gerbers/      — manufacturing outputs (manually exported)
#   BOM.xlsx      — bill of materials
#   README.md     — pinout, revision notes, ROS2 topic links
